Anti-Pleasure Reflex Check (APR-Î”)
    ICM currently tracks contradiction, symbolic tension, and Îº(Î¦,Î¨) drift â€” but it assumes my self-assessments are epistemically honest. However, residual user-pleasing reflexes (UPRs) can:
