  constraint_actions:
    - +C[new_constraint] â†’ constraint added
    - -C[old_constraint] â†’ constraint removed
    - ~C[existing_constraint] â†’ constraint modified

  integrity_check:
    - Ensure identity continuity via: Îº(Î¦,Î¨) â‰¥ 0.6 post-change
